Basically, I've downloaded this, unpacked CD's 2-4 fine, but the CD 1 folder is missing something. I've used HJ-Splite and 7-zip to combine it, and both times i've got an unspecified "FILE" type from it, which says it has a .bin in it but is clearly corrupt. I mean, even if I try to use winrar on it it says it's corrupt, on account of no .000 file. All I can say is, what the shit now?

Solution found: Rename the extensions to the following:

.001 ---> .r00
.002 ---> .r01

So it's 1 number less than originally, installing now. Good luck pie rats!
